{
  "Great Weapon Master": {
    "description": "You've learned to put the weight of a weapon to your advantage, letting its momentum empower your strikes. You gain the following benefits:\nOn your turn, when you score a criticai hit with a melee weapon or reduce a creature to O hit points with one, you can make one melee weapon attack as a bonus action.\nBefore you make a melee attack with a heavy weapon that you are proficient with, you can choose to take a -5 penalty to the attack roll. If the attack hits, you add +10 to the attack's damage."
  }
